..
.de i					\" italics (font 2)
.ie \\n(.$>0 \\&\\$3\\f2\\$1\\fP\\$2
.el .ft 2
..
.de r					\" roman (font 1)
.ft 1					\" just restore it
..
.de bi					\" bold italics (embolden font 2)
\\&\\$3\c
\\kb\\f2\\$1\\fP\\h'|\\nbu+2u'\\f2\\$1\\fP\\$2
..
.\" **********
.\" point sizes -- if argument(s), apply only to first
